oize;"		yourself! !!WebGrammar methodsFor: 'element' stamp: '1/26/2017 07:21:56'!elContent	^ (javascript / element / text nonEpsilon) star! !!WebGrammar methodsFor: 'element' stamp: '1/26/2017 07:21:56'!elementName	^ #word asPParser plus flatten! !